commit.title: Packer: install 'rsync' in the ubi-packer container
commit.message:
Packer: install 'rsync' in the ubi-packer container

The build of the image fails in AppInfra when fetching RPMs on
non-existence of rsync command.

Signed-off-by: Tomáš Hozza <thozza@redhat.com>

commit.title: test/container.registry.sh: adjust embedded image check for multi-arch
commit.message:
test/container.registry.sh: adjust embedded image check for multi-arch

With the testing fedora-minimal container image now being multi-arch,
we need to first get the image ID of the architecture-specific image and
only after that we can query the registry for the image config digest.

Signed-off-by: Tomáš Hozza <thozza@redhat.com>
